=Description=

BlockchainGov:

"This collection organizes on-chain mechanisms across seven core functions: fundraising (coordinating capital flow), allocation (distributing scarce resources), value capture (monetizing generated value), rewards and penalties (shaping incentives), exchange (trading and pricing assets), governance (structuring decision-making), and data management (managing information flow and integrity). The library represents the first attempt to systematically document these mechanisms in a structured, comparative format."

